Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Soviet troops in Cuba
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3r2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Sep 1979
Arrival of 3,000 Soviet troops in Cuba seen as provocation to US and could stall SALT talks. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less